text: Emlichheim is a Samtgemeinde ("collective municipality") in Bentheim, in Lower Saxony, Germany. Its seat is in the municipality Emlichheim. The Samtgemeinde Emlichheim has the following municipalities: # Emlichheim # Hoogstede # Laar # Ringe Category:Samtgemeinden in Lower Saxony
title: Emlichheim (Samtgemeinde)
